==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: matching
<hw>matching</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>having identical or
closely similar appearance or properties; <as>as, a pair of
<ex>matching</ex> candlesticks</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> duplicate, twin(prenominal), twinned.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Harmonious and pleasing in appearance when used
together; <as>as, a <ex>matching</ex> skirt and blouse</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> coordinated; color-coordinated.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Matchless</ent>⟦br⟧
